/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Owens recorded three tackles in the Bears' 27\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00933 exhibition win over theCincinnati BengalsSaturday.\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a MondayTikTok, however, Biles revealed that she will likely attend few Bears games this season\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094because of her post-Olympic obligations.\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know how many games I will be able to make because in a few weeks we go on tour, and if you guys are not aware, it's the Gold Over America tour.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think right now we are doing about 32 stops,\\\" Biles said.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tour, a traveling gymnastics exhibition featuring Biles and a spate of other gymnasts, is scheduled to commence Sept. 16 in Oceanside, Calif.  Chicago opens its season eight days prior against theTennessee Titans.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceanside_Transit_Center\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.824510646542029e-12, \"text\": \"Oceanside\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceanside_Transit_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceanside_Transit_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9979154410498682, \"rank\": 0.0018644982398757929, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}, {\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teen_Titans\", \"score\": 0.5913133813853196, \"rank\": 0.6909703048670323, \"text\": \"Titans\", \"types\": [\"Q38672